data.text:
FAQ - noomirapace.tumblr

- Are you from Sweden?

No, I’m from Brazil :)

- Which one of the Millennium movies is your favorite?

The Girl With The Dragon Tattoo.

- Where do you get your pictures?

There isn’t an especific site where I get them! It’s basically a lot of research! A lot! And there’s also my friend Emma who helps me with some pics!

- Is there a difference between the Millennium mini-series and the movies?

Yep! Millennium mini-series is a six-part television series based on the film trilogy. The serie is about 110 minutes longer than all the movies together.

- Where can I find the series?!

http://noomirapace.tumblr.com/post/19415134212/remainshuman-replied-to-your-post

- Is Noomi married?

She was married with Ola Rapace, but they got divorcedin 2011. They have a son called Lev :)

- Does Noomi smoke?

Yes.

- Does Noomi have a twitter?

No.

- Can I make a request?

Sure!

*Well, I think those are the most asked questions!

If the answer that you are looking for is not there, feel free to ask me anything! Don’t be shy ;)
